{"type":null,"faqId":44972,"title":"短信无法发送，或者显示正在发送如何处理？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n\"您好，短信发送失败的原因有很多，请逐一排除：<br>\nA：是否可以拨打电话，排除用户卡欠费的情况<br>\nB：检查短信中心设置是否正确（“信息 &gt; 菜单 &gt; 设置 &gt; 高级 &gt; 短信中心 &gt; 检查值”是否正确）。具体短信中心号码请咨询对应移动服务运营商。短信中心不正确会导致短信发送失败。<br>\nC：拨打运营商客服电话，咨询是否运营商禁止用户短信业务（具体表现为之前能发，突然不能发送、接收。）<br>\nD：SIM卡放到其他品牌手机上，是否可以正常发送信息，如果不可以，咨询运营商解决；<br>\nE：换一张正常的卡，测试是否可以正常发送，排查用户卡的问题。特别是用户第一次使用这张卡的时候。<br>\nF：请确认发送信息的应用是否是默认短信应用。推荐用户将原生短信应用设置为默认短信应用。\"\n<br>\n<p>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"473","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409385000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":48,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"短信发送","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}